Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵 不用那麼趕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對人家小姐太失禮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快點道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉.\N-不會 沒事的.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是讓我被發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就不可以在這了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你以後別在這邊叫我大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,連這都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,天婦羅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝就好了，我不用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一點沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那一點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-夠了…   -太少了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵子，上次那件事情辦好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你有讓組長知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,組長對此 並不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的事情組長不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還在搞那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得我最近很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐你別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們自己也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吃嗎？   -真好吃.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,樓上搬來奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我看他們倆應該關係異常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我跟他們一起搭電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,女人老實說 很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,男生好像叫女生大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力集團嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,應該不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這個公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,應該不會讓暴力集團進來住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你講
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有看過這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他們對我很粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那時爸爸做生意失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都使用很粗暴的手段對我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是難受的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我公司很忙，你在家要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其他時間我會多注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼態度啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼可能是暴力團體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那我之後會注意點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是住在樓上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,總之你要注意 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像話太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼可能是暴力集團呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是愛打小報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想趕我們走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,安分點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你有老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 你安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不准叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓自己老公知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,聽話喔，懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還是別讓老公知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想要死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛不要 舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,說你舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣老公會知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵你來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,屄屄濕掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不用忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太太來唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真淫蕩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她的嘴幫你吹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地吹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,聽話喔就沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵和你老公的雞巴，哪個大？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地吹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴好好地吹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吃到喉嚨裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,吹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次吹那麼大的雞巴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,垣掝太太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這很舒服的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,臉真色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊？太太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你真色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以講出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,頭別動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的樣子喔 小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太太怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的奶子好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,硬起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,努力吹唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,變很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地抬頭吹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吹進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好色的太太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,準備張腿開幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,偷漢子的時間終於到了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不能說不要喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他都硬很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太太過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要什麼… 老公會知道唷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太太插了唷… 舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,別掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,完全幹進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你來讓他舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的屄緊得像處女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴又來了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,趴著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,翹高屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,翹高你的騷屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,自己動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打得很痛很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉內衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.75,0:24:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.70,0:24:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,激烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.79,0:25:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,躺著插呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.77,0:26:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 老公平常不會那麼激烈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.78,0:26:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵舒服嘛 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.72,0:26:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好濕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵要射了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.80,0:26:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的奶子又白又大
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.73,0:26:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.80,0:26:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被人操屄舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.74,0:26:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.81,0:26:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.95,0:26:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能對不起老公
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.75,0:26:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,給太太射裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.83,0:26:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.83,0:27:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太太懷孕了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.70,0:27:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.78,0:27:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.31,0:27:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.05,0:27:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.79,0:27:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵的精液射進去了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.80,0:27:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.80,0:27:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,從今天開始，我們會每天過來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.74,0:27:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽話就殺了你老公
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.75,0:27:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽話呢，就沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.75,0:27:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.76,0:28:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公會怎麼樣我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.76,0:28:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己好好想清楚唷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.70,0:28:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這家還要靠你唷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.71,0:28:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老公是你的支柱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.75,0:28:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 沒精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.79,0:28:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.73,0:28:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有小孩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.80,0:28:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,應該不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.80,0:28:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了\N樓上的事情你在擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.81,0:28:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.75,0:28:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.78,0:28:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一下班就來陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.75,0:29:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.79,0:29:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.79,0:29:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.73,0:29:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.80,0:29:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.73,0:29:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不要讓你老公發現
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.77,0:29:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你來廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.74,0:29:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來了一個好男人唷
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.78,0:30:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經三年沒做愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.88,0:30:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以會激烈一點
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.72,0:30:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要多忍耐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.72,0:31:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.87,0:32:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.81,0:32:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.76,0:33:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.78,0:34:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.78,0:35:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.78,0:35:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地做喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.79,0:35:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,說了還不滿足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.80,0:35:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,別太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.73,0:35:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說今天還要加強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.77,0:35:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.78,0:35:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.78,0:35:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.72,0:35:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,才剛開始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.79,0:35:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我會好好指導你的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.81,0:36:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打開腳
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.81,0:36:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.95,0:36:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.82,0:36:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,說不要卻很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.83,0:36:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.70,0:36:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.71,0:36:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,臉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奶頭那麼硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.72,0:36:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太太好色喔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.80,0:36:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,自己想要摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.80,0:37:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.81,0:37:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.75,0:37:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.75,0:37:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.75,0:37:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴吹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.29,0:37:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.76,0:37:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.77,0:37:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,吃下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.77,0:37:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.71,0:37:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.72,0:37:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.72,0:38:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.73,0:38:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吹進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.81,0:38:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.74,0:38:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地吹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.82,0:38:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,吃進去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.76,0:38:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吹進去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.83,0:38:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太太做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.78,0:38:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.72,0:39:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.73,0:39:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.75,0:39:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.75,0:39:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.82,0:39:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.83,0:39:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,到喉嚨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.77,0:39:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這種臉太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.78,0:40:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.72,0:40:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,翹高屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.80,0:40:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,翹高不
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.81,0:40:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.81,0:40:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.75,0:40:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吹喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.82,0:40:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.77,0:41:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.98,0:41:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.31,0:41:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.79,0:41:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.74,0:41:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.75,0:41:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,白天吹老公以外的雞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.83,0:42:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老公知道會離婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.78,0:42:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.79,0:42:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.79,0:42:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼濕真淫蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.81,0:42:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.75,0:42:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這個給你唷
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.82,0:43:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太大了不
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.76,0:43:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.77,0:43:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼插呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.78,0:43:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.74,0:43:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太太馬上就插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.81,0:43:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,開始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.82,0:44:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大力點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.83,0:44:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.70,0:44:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴不可以停喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.70,0:44:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續吹
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.71,0:44:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.72,0:44:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.66,0:44:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.66,0:45:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太太怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.74,0:45:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,上下都很滿足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.75,0:45:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.62,0:45:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.83,0:45:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.63,0:45:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.64,0:45:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奶頭硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.66,0:46:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,屁眼看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.74,0:46:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.68,0:46:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太太吹其他男人的雞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.75,0:46:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,又被插舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.63,0:46:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.65,0:46:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,陰部很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.65,0:46:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好濕
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.65,0:47:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.73,0:47:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.73,0:47:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小滿快點用雞巴插太太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.75,0:47:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,幫太太
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.69,0:47:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,翹高
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.63,0:47:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太太插了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.64,0:47:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.65,0:48:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.65,0:48:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.66,0:48:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.67,0:48:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,陰部都被塞滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.88,0:48:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.75,0:48:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小滿激烈插他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.69,0:48:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對 好
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.63,0:48:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很享受吧 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.72,0:49:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.66,0:49:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太太臉好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.67,0:49:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.68,0:49:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.89,0:49:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼可愛的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.62,0:49:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,陰部很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.70,0:50:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.43,0:50:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.70,0:50:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,別忍耐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.71,0:50:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服的話可以叫出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.72,0:50:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,太太也舔一下我的陰部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.65,0:50:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.66,0:50:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.73,0:50:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.67,0:50:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舔進去陰部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.67,0:50:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.67,0:50:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還不討厭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.68,0:50:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,前後都很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.69,0:51:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.70,0:51:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭出來點
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.64,0:51:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,激烈點
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.65,0:51:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.65,0:51:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣還不賴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.66,0:51:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.67,0:51:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.74,0:51:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.74,0:51:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續舔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.68,0:52:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.75,0:52:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.62,0:52:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,做得很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.70,0:52:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒經驗過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.71,0:52:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,對 繼續地插他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.72,0:52:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對 越來越濕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.73,0:52:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣？舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.68,0:53:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.75,0:53:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.71,0:53:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.85,0:53:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,現在樓上的來打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.72,0:53:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.66,0:53:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.68,0:54:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.68,0:54:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在講小孩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.62,0:54:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才可以容易懷孕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.63,0:54:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說她老公很快讓她懷孕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.71,0:54:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那你小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.73,0:54:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小滿，你射多點到太太屄裡
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.67,0:55:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要讓太太肚子大起來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.66,0:55:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.63,0:55:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.71,0:55:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.92,0:55:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.45,0:55:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.72,0:55:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看著
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.67,0:56:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.75,0:56:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.76,0:56:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.71,0:56:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.65,0:57:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.69,0:57:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,射了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.70,0:57:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-射裡面喔…  -不
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.73,0:58:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太太到時可能會懷孕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.74,0:58:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過老公不會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.68,0:58:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要看著你老公開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.63,0:58:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,讓昨天那男人舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.74,0:58:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我會帶另外一個來給你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.67,0:59:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他很久沒舒服過了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.68,0:59:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不讓他舒服的話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.68,0:59:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會被殺掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.70,0:59:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.71,0:59:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.66,1:00:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,趴著
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.75,1:00:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.91,1:00:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.72,1:01:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,過來替我吹
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.67,1:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,吹啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.75,1:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.74,1:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.71,1:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.63,1:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.64,1:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.72,1:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.72,1:04:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.69,1:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.62,1:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦 放過我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.70,1:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.72,1:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦 放過我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.73,1:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.74,1:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.67,1:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.69,1:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.64,1:08:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.68,1:10:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.75,1:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.69,1:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.63,1:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.65,1:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.66,1:11:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.02,1:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.23,1:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.64,1:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.98,1:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.73,1:12:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.74,1:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.63,1:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.68,1:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.69,1:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.63,1:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.71,1:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.72,1:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.80,1:16:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.74,1:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.68,1:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了唷
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.75,1:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.75,1:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.63,1:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,射喔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.64,1:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.75,1:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.00,1:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太太越來越舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.07,1:17:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,其實很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.07,1:17:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,說出來沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.08,1:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,臉好色喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.09,1:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.09,1:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.10,1:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你們夫婦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.10,1:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最好乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.10,1:18:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.17,1:18:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不然不可能活在這世上的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.11,1:18:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你安靜地給我過來
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.18,1:18:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.12,1:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就在那邊看你太太舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.06,1:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的巨乳人氣很高喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.06,1:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.74,1:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.14,1:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.74,1:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.07,1:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.34,1:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.08,1:19:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.15,1:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.22,1:19:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.09,1:19:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的太太
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.09,1:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在眼前做愛
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.10,1:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.10,1:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.10,1:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,說不要
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.10,1:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,卻還硬起來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.11,1:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.11,1:19:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有點變硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.12,1:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看著
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.13,1:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.13,1:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.13,1:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.14,1:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在她老公面前
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.07,1:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,狠狠上他老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.14,1:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,給這位先生清楚地看著
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.16,1:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.10,1:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.31,1:20:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.51,1:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.91,1:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.18,1:20:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.18,1:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.18,1:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.65,1:20:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.52,1:20:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.12,1:21:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.33,1:21:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要幹我
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.06,1:21:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.07,1:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.14,1:21:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很淫蕩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.14,1:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.14,1:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.15,1:21:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,硬硬的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.15,1:21:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還想要舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.09,1:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.03,1:21:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.16,1:21:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公雞巴變好硬喔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.10,1:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看自己老婆被人強姦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.17,1:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,變那麼硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.11,1:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公在想什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.18,1:21:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.12,1:22:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看老婆被人姦，這麼舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.06,1:22:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴變那麼大
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.07,1:22:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜歡看老婆被人操吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.14,1:22:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.14,1:22:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.14,1:22:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公不要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.15,1:22:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.15,1:22:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.09,1:22:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.23,1:22:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.10,1:22:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.10,1:22:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.11,1:22:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看著你老婆喔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.18,1:23:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先生的雞巴，好像很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.12,1:23:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也該上場了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.06,1:23:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你老婆看著
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.13,1:23:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟其他女人做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.14,1:23:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都這麼硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.14,1:23:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就可以操屄了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.07,1:23:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.08,1:23:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.08,1:23:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.09,1:23:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能上她
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.09,1:23:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老公\N想要插更好的屄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.09,1:23:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,說 你想要插啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.10,1:23:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不說的話
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.10,1:23:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你太太會更舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.10,1:24:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.11,1:24:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.11,1:24:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那插進去了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.12,1:24:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.12,1:24:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！放過我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.13,1:24:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.13,1:24:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公的雞巴好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.14,1:24:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.07,1:24:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.14,1:24:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.14,1:24:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.15,1:24:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.15,1:24:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.16,1:24:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的陰部
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.16,1:24:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.16,1:25:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你太太誰好呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.17,1:25:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太太仔細看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.18,1:25:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公的雞巴也好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.11,1:25:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.19,1:25:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.13,1:25:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒做愛了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.06,1:25:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.27,1:25:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊啊 太太
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.07,1:25:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.08,1:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的騷屄
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.08,1:25:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,比起來 還是我的屄更好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.09,1:25:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 不
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.09,1:26:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.10,1:26:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老公好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.17,1:26:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.17,1:26:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.18,1:26:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.18,1:26:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太太我可以高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.11,1:26:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看喔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.12,1:26:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要高潮了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.12,1:26:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.06,1:26:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.14,1:26:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.09,1:27:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.09,1:27:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,老公\N你讓我很舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.10,1:27:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,被老婆看著偷情，很興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.17,1:27:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.17,1:27:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.11,1:27:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.19,1:27:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,現在該你了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.12,1:27:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.13,1:27:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.13,1:27:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在眼前被強姦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.06,1:27:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你要射出來喔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.13,1:27:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.14,1:27:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行喔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.14,1:27:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴都那麼硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.14,1:28:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.08,1:28:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直說他想射喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.15,1:28:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,太太看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.09,1:28:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他想要射喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.16,1:28:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.16,1:28:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他要射出來了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.10,1:28:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.10,1:28:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.17,1:28:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己也正跟其他男人操屄啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.18,1:28:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太太，被人操很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.25,1:28:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴好硬喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.12,1:28:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.12,1:28:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你老婆被人強姦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.13,1:28:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.07,1:28:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.07,1:29:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你太太被操得好騷浪喔
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.08,1:29:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在自己老婆的眼前
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.08,1:29:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,痛快射精吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.15,1:29:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,變硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.15,1:29:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太太看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.16,1:29:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.16,1:29:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 太太看著
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.10,1:29:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好色情啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.10,1:29:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.18,1:29:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太太看著哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.18,1:29:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公這樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.12,1:29:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.19,1:29:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,說你的雞巴很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.13,1:29:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老公啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.33,1:29:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.86,1:30:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.33,1:30:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,自己老婆被人強姦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.14,1:30:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.07,1:30:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她整個騷屄都濕了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.15,1:30:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛忍耐啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.16,1:30:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太太看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.36,1:30:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.10,1:30:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在太太面前射精吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.17,1:30:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦？到底怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.11,1:30:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想射了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.12,1:30:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.12,1:30:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-太太仔細看啊   -不
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.06,1:31:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公的雞巴 和現在的雞巴
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.13,1:31:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡哪個
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.07,1:31:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你太太好像很舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.14,1:31:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.14,1:31:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太太你老公要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.08,1:31:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了喔\N老公
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.15,1:31:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看喔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.16,1:31:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.23,1:31:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公射那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.17,1:31:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一定很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.18,1:32:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.19,1:32:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太太也看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.12,1:32:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.13,1:32:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.13,1:32:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.07,1:32:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.07,1:32:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫我舔乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.07,1:32:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公插過的陰部
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.08,1:32:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.15,1:32:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,舔乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.09,1:32:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的陰部怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.09,1:32:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,濕濕的陰部
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.10,1:32:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.10,1:32:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.11,1:32:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.11,1:33:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.11,1:33:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行喔
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.12,1:33:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老公雞巴的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.19,1:33:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.06,1:33:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,味道棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.33,1:33:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.07,1:33:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,上下的嘴巴都有了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.08,1:33:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.08,1:33:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.16,1:33:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.16,1:33:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.10,1:33:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你知道下場吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.10,1:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.10,1:34:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,舔乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.17,1:34:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.31,1:34:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.24,1:34:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.18,1:34:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舔乾淨喔
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.13,1:34:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.07,1:34:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太太難道你要高潮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.08,1:34:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公在看著喔
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.15,1:34:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.15,1:34:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.15,1:34:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-高潮去吧  -老公別看
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.30,1:35:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵在老公面前
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.10,1:35:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.17,1:35:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,射精出來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.11,1:35:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,讓太太替你生個大胖小子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.12,1:35:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老公不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.12,1:35:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.13,1:35:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.13,1:35:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看啦
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.13,1:35:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.07,1:35:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.54,1:35:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.07,1:35:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.15,1:35:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵射了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.09,1:36:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.16,1:36:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一定會懷孕的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.16,1:36:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老公看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.17,1:36:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都有不同的男人插進去
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.11,1:36:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太太真的很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.18,1:36:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉老公
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.12,1:36:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太太老公我帶走了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.06,1:36:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我做過的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.07,1:36:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,都屬於我的喔
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.07,1:36:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小鐵帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.34,1:36:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.08,1:36:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公不
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.08,1:36:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公拜託
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.15,1:37:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.09,1:37:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.09,1:37:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.09,1:37:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我還會帶不同男人來喔
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.16,1:37:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要好好服務喔
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.16,1:37:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼多多指教了喔\N
